I believe it was my son's comment that he thought I was a happier mom when I was reading.  I made me realize how much I really loved a good book.  I really want others to experience the love of a good book!  I think it is amazing how wonderful it can be to unleash your imagination in the pages of a good book!  I hope that you find my book recommendations and reviews helpful in choosing your next book!\r\n
